{
  "stem": "3341.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father was very angry, and without telling me what he wanted to do, he, through his connections in the-- in the new business, which he had already for some time, in the ladies' and mens' fashion-- That was his new business?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "New business, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he had lot of friends who-- who were manufacturer, especially in the other part of Czechoslovakia because Moravia was the nearest country.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Moravians are Czech, speaking Czech.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Czech and Slovak, for instance-- the two languages are completely different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I-- I remember the the first teachers or professors in my high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were mostly Czechs, because Slovakia was under 1,000 years of occupation of Hungarian, Austro-Hungarian empire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Bohemia and Moravia was under the influence of the culture influence of Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my professors were mainly Czech because the Slovaks didn't have a-- a crop of teachers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it has got significance later on in my life, which I didn't realize as a child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this influence of-- of Czech teacher taught me maybe in a better quality teachings than the Slovak teachers would have because they had to learn themselves first.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And under such circumstances, I-- I was quite happy in any school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I went to the [NON-ENGLISH] [INAUDIBLE] if I wanted to be in the-- in the dramatic art, it would have changed my life, of course.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father got in touch, without telling me, of course-- because in that time, a child of 14 or 15 was considered as a child.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you would not ask what you want to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were told what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he arranged through his connections in the other part of Czechoslovakia with a manufacturer who was a big manufacturer for textiles.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
